 a consistent model for the\ndescription of the formation of asymmetric propellers caused by a freely moving\nmoonlet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2018 23:56:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
